      "id": "sched_weekly_lbl",
      "x": 650,
      "y": 1258,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 90,
      "text": "weekly-progress-digest  [cron: 0 9 * * 0]  dispatch_mode: prompt\nLLM reads analytics snapshots for past 7 days across all active maps\n→ identifies trends: velocity, retention rates, struggling areas\n→ highlights achievements: mastered nodes, streaks, improvements\n→ flags retention_rate_7d < 0.60 or struggling_nodes >= 3\n→ notify(channel=\"telegram\", intent=\"send\", message=<digest>)",
